OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers
OL,6,Fcontinuing across parts of England and
OL,7,FWales, especially towards the west
OL,8,Fwhere they will become heavier and
OL,9,Fpossibly thundery. Turning drier for
OL,10,Fmuch of Northern Ireland and Scotland,
OL,11,Fwith clearer skies leading to some
OL,12,Fpatchy fog.
OL,13,
OL,14,CMonday:FSunshine and showers for many
OL,15,Ftomorrow, with a band of more
OL,16,Fpersistent rain moving into Northern
OL,17,FIreland, Wales and southwest England
OL,18,Fby evening. Temperatures near or a
OL,19,Flittle below average.
